{
  "texts": [
    "Similarly, Kresevic et al.",
    "showed that RAG technology could significantly enhance LLM performance in liver disease, increasing the accuracy from 43-99% 21.",
    "Similarly, another study has shown that agent-based RAG technology with a brain rehabilitation knowledge base significantly improves LLM responses 22.",
    "In otolaryngology, RAG technology has been shown to reduce the error rate of LLM responses by 58.4% 26.",
    "These results are consistent with those of the present study."
  ]
}